{
  "id": "RAW_c087cf03",
  "title": "JoyAgent 团队 GAIA 技术报告出炉了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450154&idx=2&sn=e0bb588b28782c9f4dbb7d1ade5f50e4",
  "date": "2025-10-25 13:18:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:20px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;\">JoyAgent-JDGenie：京东团队打造的新一代通用智能体框架，GAIA 评测表现惊艳！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">随着大语言模型（LLM）能力的不断增强，人们不再满足于“会聊天的模型”，而是希望它们能成为真正的“智能体”——能规划、能行动、能记忆、能适应复杂任务。然而，目前大多数系统都在“局部优化”：加工具、调提示、改策略，却缺乏一个统一、鲁棒、可扩展的框架。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">京东团队最新发布的&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">JoyAgent-JDGenie</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">，为了解决这一问题，提出了一个系统级的通用智能体架构，在 GAIA 基准测试中取得了&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Pass@1 75.2%、Pass@3 82.4%</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;的优异成绩，超越了所有开源系统，逼近闭源顶尖框架！</span></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-top:0.5px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);font-variant-caps:normal;border-right:none;white-space:normal;border-image:initial;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;border-left:none;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;border-bottom:none;text-transform:none;margin-bottom:16px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">🧠 核心架构：三大组件构建强大智能体</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">JoyAgent 的成功不是“堆模型”，而是靠系统级设计。其架构由三大核心组成：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000129\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:392px;height:238px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3621b0fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fb4vfljQMggAvI9pcibiaZ2GQdk2aMyBia1riaxlzmPtf3Gglfw0KsqvRASeZR8wibw4RU3IQ8ndxZMuuHvgO6ic6bmSQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 多智能体协同框架（Multi-Agent Ensemble）</span></h3>\n  <ul style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:disc;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;margin:0px 0px 12px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">融合&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Plan–Execute（计划-执行）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;与&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">ReAct（推理-行动）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;两种智能体范式。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;margin:0px 0px 12px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">通过“</span></span><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">后置投票机制</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">”融合多个智能体的输出，兼顾稳定性与灵活性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">引入“</span></span><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">监督智能体</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">”确保全局一致性，避免“各自为政”。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 分层记忆系统（Hierarchical Memory）</span></h3>\n  <ul style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:disc;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">工作记忆</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">：保存当前任务的上下文、工具输出、消息交互。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">语义记忆</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">：压缩历史任务经验，支持跨任务知识迁移。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;\">\n    <p><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">程序记忆</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">：通过动态调整系统提示，指导智能体如何规划、判断、应对冲突。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-right-style:initial;font-variant-caps:normal;border-bottom-color:initial;white-space:normal;border-image:initial;font-weight:400;border-left-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;quotes:none;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;border-left-style:solid;font-variant-emoji:inherit;border-top-color:initial;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;border-width:0px 0px 0px 3.5px;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 1em;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;border-right-color:initial;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;border-top-style:initial;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;border-bottom-style:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">这套记忆系统让智能体在长时间、多轮交互中保持“身份一致性”和“经验积累”。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:26px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 精简但强大的工具集（Curated Tool Suite）</span></h3>\n  <ul style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;list-style:disc;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.5px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:inherit;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;margin:0px 0px 12px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">聚焦三大核心能力：</span></span><strong style=\"font-family: inherit;scrollbar-color: transparent transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-style: inherit;font-variant: inherit;font-weight: 600;font-stretch: inherit;font-size: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-optical-sizing: inherit;font-size-adjust: inherit;font-kerning: inherit;font-feature-settings: inherit;font-variation-settings: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 