://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">critic model 见系统图，本质是判别融合模型用于判断判别哪个答案是正确的。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000130\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2824074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91064b62&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fb4vfljQMggAvI9pcibiaZ2GQdk2aMyBia1r0wQa9ibicT8xM7IXGrTLltelZtVAibllsEGmphLicHpiaPfuCoorfIoHq4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-top:0.5px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13);font-variant-caps:normal;border-right:none;white-space:normal;border-image:initial;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;border-left:none;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;border-bottom:none;text-transform:none;margin-bottom:16px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-variant-east-asian:inherit;font-variation-settings:inherit;font-variant-position:inherit;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;font-variant-alternates:inherit;scrollbar-color:transparent transparent;text-indent:0px;font-variant-emoji:inherit;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric:inherit;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;border:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0px;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:28px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;font-stretch:inherit;font-kerning:inherit;font-optical-sizing:inherit;text-transform:none;font-size-adjust:inherit;font-feature-settings:inherit;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \\&quot;Noto Sans\\&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Source Han Sans SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, sans-serif; scrollbar-color: transparent transparent; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">🧩&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">tricks</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">1.课程学习</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">在优化算法前，我们基于主流开源 Agent 算法进行批量实验，根据模型的实际执行难度（平均成功率）重新标记任务的 task level，得到模型一致的数据难度分布阶梯；有利于课程学习，即 Agent 先完成简单任务并积累对应的代码片段记忆（semantic memory），逐步形成滚雪球效应；</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000133\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"301\" style=\"width: 403px;height: 301px;\" width=\"403\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ad7ca359&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fb4vfljQMggAvI9pcibiaZ2GQdk2aMyBia1r7jctKznmu0DlSbsLdLZRBKmBaLYCJgqksfEltMvv9x26h9p5Ehq0kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000132\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7185185185185186\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"289\" style=\"width: 403px;height: 289px;\" width=\"403\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=921cb74c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fb4vfljQMggAvI9pcibiaZ2GQdk2aMyBia1rejbIN9369Us5saG1EVRdXgFM2w7c60Dgrj0XiaNzuzZRWkicfum1LgpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">2.任务退避：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;\">（1）任务的执行顺序已经由</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;\">重估计后的难度</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;\">进行重排（2）当某个任务失败后，将其退后</span></span><code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;\">k=10</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;\">个直到不能再退后，以保证智能体可以在学习与进化后重新挑战；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">3.多模型多采样广泛实验：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">（1）先针对每个 task 样本超参数进行 grid search（例如某个任务在&nbsp;</span></span><code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">claude-4-sonnet</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;结合高温&nbsp;</span></span><code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">0.8</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;时可以正确回答），即单链路实验（2）在多链路采样上，尽可能保证同模型或同温度（3）完成一批任务后，如&nbsp;</span></span><code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">batch = 25</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">，根据 task intent 聚类分布与超参数分布的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">联合分布</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">，对后续任务的模型超参数进行优化，即从该联合分布进行采样；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">4.工具一致性控制：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">随着实验的推移，不断降低原 semantic memory 检索占比，同时适当增大（或不改变）新生成（成功经验学习）的 episodic memory 的占比，从而推动 developer 智能体代码生成分布的演进；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">5.人在环路指导（后期）：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">随着任务难度达到 level 3 以上，模型会经常受挫，此时，对任意的子智能体，靠近初始时刻的</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">决策重要性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">往往大于后续决策（好的开始是成功的一半）；因此，可以必要地在任务执行前提供一些指导（请注意，这些</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">指导不属于作弊</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">）；具体而言，我们明确规定指导暂时只有一种，即提供一指向外部第三方代码库或知识文档的 URL 以及说明&nbsp;</span></span><code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">(URL, description)</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">，以更好地、更准确地导航智能体的工具知识获取与利用</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: normal;\">论文具体见JoyAgent-JDGenie: Technical Report on the GAIA</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: normal;\">项目代码见</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/jd-opensource/joyagent-jdgenie\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/jd-opensource/joyagent-jdgenie</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "京东 JoyAgent-JDGenie 框架通过多智能体协同、分层记忆和精简工具集，在 GAIA 评测中取得优异成绩，为通用智能体开发提供系统级方案。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "京东 JoyAgent-JDGenie 框架通过多智能体协同、分层记忆和精简工具集，在 GAIA 评测中取得优异成绩，为通用智能体开发提供系统级方案。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了京东团队研发的 JoyAgent-JDGenie 通用智能体框架，旨在解决当前大语言模型（LLM）在复杂任务中缺乏统一、鲁棒、可扩展架构的问题。该框架由三大核心组件构成：多智能体协同框架（融合 Plan-Execute 与 ReAct 范式，通过后置投票和监督智能体确保全局一致性）、分层记忆系统（包括工作记忆、语义记忆和程序记忆，支持经验积累与跨任务知识迁移）以及精简工具集（聚焦搜索、代码执行和多模态解析）。JoyAgent 在 GAIA 通用 AI 助手评测基准中取得了 Pass@1 75.2%、Pass@3 82.4%的优异成绩，超越所有开源系统并逼近闭源顶尖框架，验证了其系统级设计的有效性。文章还分享了课程学习、任务退避等多项优化技巧，为智能体性能提升提供了实践指导。",
